eu.bavenir.ogwapi.restapi.services

Class ObjectsOid

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.restlet.resource.Resource
      • org.restlet.resource.ServerResource
        • eu.bavenir.ogwapi.restapi.services.ObjectsOid

  • public class ObjectsOid
extends org.restlet.resource.ServerResource
    This class implements a ServerResource interface for following Gateway API calls: URL: [server]:[port]/api/objects/{oid} METHODS: GET SPECIFICATION: @see Gateway API ATTRIBUTES: oid - VICINITY identifier of the object (e.g. 0729a580-2240-11e6-9eb5-0002a5d5c51b).
    Author:
    Andrej
